Quote: Annually more and more stories would be added to the rich collection of folklore tales about the Coast and its 'bait, suitable white pine trees for hand net poles, lesser supplejacks in the bush, new paint and timber for spotter boards, and sadly much of the gear went down the river in times of high flooding ...
